{
  "stem": "2804.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- and when we drove up to Dachau, as I said, when we went into Dachau, the gates there, and we came into this very, very large compound, court.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One side was a-- it looked like a hotel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we found out that the German officers stayed there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On another side, there were barracks where the German-- I guess the GIs there stayed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they had warehouses, which later-- a couple days later when we walked over to them and walked in, looked like they plundered Europe.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You-- we found everything and anything, that-- where they accumulated all these things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were paintings.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was one warehouse just filled with material and with cottons, spools of cotton, every conceivable type of a material that you would want.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had-- well, they had some of the-- some of the survivors there work as-- in leather goods, where they had them make shoes and had them-- of course, there were machines there with leather goods.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They had-- well, there we found also some of the lampshades that Ilse Koch had taken from the skins of the people there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just the soldiers that went in two days before to liberate the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they just went in and, you know, they didn't stay, because they-- and we went in right after them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I said, we saw this compound and we saw the-- this hotel and we saw the hotel-like building.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And to the right, when we went in, was this compound that was wired off with people clinging to it, yelling, carrying on, calling in all different languages.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
